<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>About — LS Clip</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
</head>
<body data-theme="white">
<div class="app">

<header>
  <a class="logo" href="/">
    <div class="logo-mark">&#8249;LS&#8250;</div>
    <div>
      <div class="brand-title">Clip</div>
      <div class="brand-sub">Logic Shift</div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <div class="header-right">
    <a class="nav-link" href="/help">Help</a>
    <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
    <div class="theme-toggle">
      <button class="theme-btn active" data-theme="white" onclick="LSClip.setTheme('white')">White</button>
      <button class="theme-btn" data-theme="dark" onclick="LSClip.setTheme('dark')">Dark</button>
      <button class="theme-btn" data-theme="paper" onclick="LSClip.setTheme('paper')">Paper</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="content-page fade-in">
    <h2>About Us</h2>

    <p><b>Logic Shift</b> &mdash; solo-built tools for everyday problems.</p>
    <p>LS Clip is a small, self-hosted utility made to share text, notes, and files quickly without friction. No sign-ups, no tracking, no bloat.</p>

    <div style="margin:32px 0;padding:24px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius);">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:16px;">
        <div class="logo-mark" style="width:48px;height:48px;font-size:16px;">&#8249;LS&#8250;</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-size:20px;font-weight:800;">LS Clip</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);">Logic Shift Clip</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-muted);">A minimal, professional clipboard/snippet sharing web app. Built with Node.js, Express, SQLite, and TipTap. Self-hosted and open source.</p>
    </div>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pick a custom slug (or use a random one) to create a clip.</li>
      <li>Write or paste your content &mdash; rich text, code, notes, or links.</li>
      <li>Share the URL. Anyone with the link can view (or edit, depending on access mode).</li>
      <li>Clips expire automatically. Rolling expiry keeps active clips alive.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Tech Stack</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><b>Backend:</b> Node.js, Express, SQLite (sql.js)</li>
      <li><b>Frontend:</b> Vanilla JS, EJS templates, TipTap editor</li>
      <li><b>Security:</b> bcryptjs, express-rate-limit, Cloudflare Turnstile</li>
      <li><b>Deployment:</b> Docker, docker-compose</li>
    </ul>

    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-subtle);margin-top:32px;">This is a placeholder. Full about content will be provided later.</p>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <span>Self-hosted &middot; Minimal &middot; Open Source</span>
  <span></span>
</footer>

</div>

<div id="toasts"></div>
<script src="/js/app.js"></script>
<script>LSClip.init({ BASE_URL: '<%= BASE_URL %>' });</script>
</body>
</html>